    "description": "<p><strong>DIS Manpower Pte Ltd</strong> is a Licensed Employment Agency (EA License No. 08C3226) since 2007 with the vision of becoming one of the top manpower-cum-recruitment companies in Singapore, providing permanent placements and executive-search services for highly trained hospitality professionals to the tourism and hospitality industry and beyond. As a professional manpower employment agency, DIS seeks to provide absolute precision in staffing, manpower and human resource solutions. Coupled with a team of well-experienced recruiters and outstanding employment services, candidates can be markedly assured of our dedication to secure felicitous job positions for them. Mutually beneficial to both clients and candidates, DIS assists to deploy appointed candidates into our client organisations and at the same time, focuses on helping candidates source for a fruitful career.</p>    <p>Till date, DIS has successfully bridged many talented candidates to their ideal organisations within a short frame of time.</p>    <p> </p>  ",
